8. Model module
---------------
The copy constructors of the GModelSpatialDiffuse, GModelSpatialElliptical
and GModelSpatialRadial classes did not properly copy the base class members
in their copy constructors. This prevented specifically the fitting of
diffuse maps in the stacked analysis. The code was modified to fix the
issue.


